WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:01:33.190 --> 00:01:34.990
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

3
00:01:34.990 --> 00:01:37.950
Curry Mix

4
00:01:34.990 --> 00:01:37.950
Curry Mix

5
00:01:40.250 --> 00:01:41.400
All right, then.

6
00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:44.160
Let's begin making the torture implement.

7
00:01:44.160 --> 00:01:47.220
Yes! I'm ready to learn!

8
00:01:54.630 --> 00:01:56.620
Form a claw with your left hand.

9
00:01:57.120 --> 00:02:00.330
Cut the carrots 
into one-centimeter rounds.

10
00:02:03.100 --> 00:02:04.600
Say, Sakura-chan.

11
00:02:04.600 --> 00:02:05.460
Yes?

12
00:02:05.870 --> 00:02:10.100
Have you considered applying to become 
a pain-private in the near future?

13
00:02:10.100 --> 00:02:11.440
What?!

14
00:02:11.440 --> 00:02:15.660
Your training period's about to end, 
so I think it's the perfect time.

15
00:02:17.850 --> 00:02:22.160
I'm not a demon, so do 
I stand any chance of getting in?

16
00:02:22.160 --> 00:02:22.990
Most certainly.

17
00:02:23.560 --> 00:02:27.410
I've seen all of the hard 
work you've been putting in.

18
00:02:32.410 --> 00:02:35.090
Me, an inquisitor...

19
00:02:35.330 --> 00:02:37.870
There's no need to fret so much.

20
00:02:38.230 --> 00:02:43.900
To become a pain-private, simply submit
 the form with all the required fields.

21
00:02:44.350 --> 00:02:45.860
Oh, that said...

22
00:02:45.860 --> 00:02:50.040
The application requires that you write 
down a torture you're proficient in.

23
00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:51.310
What will you choose?

24
00:02:51.730 --> 00:02:53.590
Anything in particular you fancy?

25
00:02:55.060 --> 00:02:56.230
Actually...

26
00:02:56.570 --> 00:03:00.190
There's one torture I wanted to try.

27
00:03:00.570 --> 00:03:02.660
Oh? What is it?

28
00:03:03.490 --> 00:03:06.930
Senpai, do you have 
some free time tomorrow?

29
00:03:06.930 --> 00:03:07.800
Tomorrow?

30
00:03:08.650 --> 00:03:12.330
I'd like to give it a shot 
before I fill everything out...

31
00:03:12.330 --> 00:03:17.520
Or well, I want you to take 
a look at my torture...

32
00:03:18.210 --> 00:03:22.460
I want you to be my first torture victim!

33
00:03:24.310 --> 00:03:26.050
'Twould be an honor!

34
00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:29.980
Sakura's
 Apartment

35
00:03:33.270 --> 00:03:37.400
<i>All my life, I've done nothing 
but obey orders.</i>

36
00:03:38.260 --> 00:03:42.100
<i>I never gave any thought 
as to what I wanted.</i>

37
00:03:43.270 --> 00:03:48.980
<i>The only thing I knew was assassination, 
and all I could do was make people suffer.</i>

38
00:03:49.330 --> 00:03:53.740
<i>I never imagined I could be cut out 
to entertain them through torture.</i>

39
00:03:55.230 --> 00:03:56.280
<i>However...</i>

40
00:03:57.520 --> 00:04:00.330
<i>after learning about torture from Senpai,</i>

41
00:04:01.210 --> 00:04:05.570
<i>she made me realize all the 
different things I was capable of doing.</i>

42
00:04:09.670 --> 00:04:12.510
<i>Take a good look, Senpai...</i>

43
00:04:12.950 --> 00:04:17.520
<i>at what I've chosen 
for the first time, all by myself.</i>

44
00:04:18.050 --> 00:04:20.040
<i>My first torture.</i>

45
00:04:28.410 --> 00:04:31.530
Senpai, it's time for your torture!

46
00:04:31.530 --> 00:04:33.990
My street performance torture...

47
00:04:34.330 --> 00:04:36.000
Please enjoy it!

48
00:04:53.260 --> 00:04:55.510
Where'd that apple come from?

49
00:04:59.970 --> 00:05:00.820
What?!

50
00:05:05.990 --> 00:05:10.580
<i>She's keeping the apple in the air by 
throwing the knives she's juggling at it,</i>

51
00:05:10.580 --> 00:05:12.540
<i>while peeling it at the same time?!</i>

52
00:05:16.050 --> 00:05:16.950
S...

53
00:05:17.340 --> 00:05:19.340
Sakura-chan, that was amazing!

54
00:05:25.540 --> 00:05:26.550
Huh?

55
00:05:26.550 --> 00:05:29.140
Wait... Surely not...

56
00:05:29.640 --> 00:05:31.720
You were still saving your best trick?!

57
00:05:42.680 --> 00:05:43.230
Hah!

58
00:05:45.020 --> 00:05:47.480
Wow!

59
00:05:49.700 --> 00:05:52.880
Senpai! What'd you think of my torture?

60
00:05:52.880 --> 00:05:55.310
That was incredible, Sakura-chan.

61
00:05:55.310 --> 00:05:58.490
It was so thrilling, 
I almost forgot it was torture!

62
00:05:58.790 --> 00:06:00.990
I really enjoyed it!

63
00:06:07.260 --> 00:06:09.400
Thanks a lot!

64
00:06:10.390 --> 00:06:15.350
Sakura's pain-private
 application

65
00:06:12.640 --> 00:06:15.350
Was submitted

66
00:06:16.850 --> 00:06:18.300
Princess...

67
00:06:18.860 --> 00:06:20.860
Your torture's been canceled.

68
00:06:20.860 --> 00:06:21.910
Huh?

69
00:06:21.910 --> 00:06:23.860
What's the meaning of this?

70
00:06:24.110 --> 00:06:26.840
Remember our conversation the other day ?

71
00:06:28.390 --> 00:06:29.490
Oh, yeah.

72
00:06:29.820 --> 00:06:33.520
What animals do you like 
that haven't shown up in a torture yet?

73
00:06:35.510 --> 00:06:36.950
Penguins!

74
00:06:36.950 --> 00:06:42.600
So I asked a penguin I know to come all 
the way here for today's torture...

75
00:06:39.080 --> 00:06:44.840
Hellbeast Penguin

76
00:06:39.080 --> 00:06:44.840
Hellbeast Penguin

77
00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:46.240
But we've been having 
a nasty heatwave in Hellholm,

78
00:06:46.240 --> 00:06:48.870
so he can't make it.

79
00:06:48.870 --> 00:06:52.010
Hellbeast penguins don't 
do well in the heat.

80
00:06:52.010 --> 00:06:53.640
Poor thing!

81
00:06:53.640 --> 00:06:57.850
That's a shame, but 
the penguin's health comes first.

82
00:06:57.850 --> 00:06:59.630
Thanks, Princess.

83
00:06:59.630 --> 00:07:03.900
Your Highness, you like penguins 
as well as hamsters?

84
00:07:03.900 --> 00:07:04.910
Yeah.

85
00:07:05.500 --> 00:07:07.510
The way they waddle.

86
00:07:07.510 --> 00:07:08.960
Their cute, round eyes.

87
00:07:08.960 --> 00:07:10.930
Their gentle faces.

88
00:07:10.930 --> 00:07:15.410
I fell in love with them at a penguin show
I saw at the aquarium as a kid.

89
00:07:15.800 --> 00:07:17.410
Penguins!

90
00:07:17.410 --> 00:07:19.160
Penguins!

91
00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:22.460
Penguin Show

92
00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:21.200
Seeing them shuffle to and fro.

93
00:07:21.200 --> 00:07:23.360
Cheering them on when they mess up.

94
00:07:22.470 --> 00:07:24.280
Get up! You can do it!

95
00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:25.750
Their laid-back attitudes.

96
00:07:24.280 --> 00:07:26.690
Pick yourself back up!

97
00:07:25.740 --> 00:07:27.890
So adorable.

98
00:07:28.940 --> 00:07:34.010
Penjamin couldn't make it, but he's 
the Northern Demon World Aquarium's star!

99
00:07:34.010 --> 00:07:35.680
Oh, wow.

100
00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:37.290
The cream of the crop, huh?

101
00:07:37.290 --> 00:07:40.310
I'll have him come some 
other time when it's cooler.

102
00:07:40.310 --> 00:07:41.510
Yeah!

103
00:07:41.870 --> 00:07:44.260
I can't wait to meet him!

104
00:07:44.640 --> 00:07:46.290
Hold your horses!

105
00:07:47.320 --> 00:07:48.720
Some other time?

106
00:07:48.720 --> 00:07:51.230
You can't be serious, ladies.

107
00:07:53.090 --> 00:07:55.700
The hellbeast penguin, Penjamin...

108
00:07:56.830 --> 00:07:59.410
is right here, baby!

109
00:07:59.410 --> 00:08:01.580
What? Penjamin?!

110
00:08:01.580 --> 00:08:04.470
Sorry I'm a teensy bit late.

111
00:08:05.210 --> 00:08:06.860
You're covered in sweat!

112
00:08:06.860 --> 00:08:09.620
You came all this way in this heat?

113
00:08:10.450 --> 00:08:14.900
No heat's gonna stop me 
from helping out my buddy Krall!

114
00:08:15.470 --> 00:08:17.100
Penjamin!

115
00:08:17.420 --> 00:08:19.200
Alrighty, Krall.

116
00:08:19.200 --> 00:08:21.910
We can't keep our 
audience waiting any longer.

117
00:08:21.910 --> 00:08:23.890
Time to look alive.

118
00:08:24.840 --> 00:08:28.670
Let's get this penguin show on the road!

119
00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:32.650
The Penjamin Show

120
00:08:32.650 --> 00:08:36.320
The Penjamin Show

121
00:08:36.900 --> 00:08:39.570
First up, we have this trick!

122
00:08:39.570 --> 00:08:42.070
A-one, a-two, a-three!

123
00:08:45.790 --> 00:08:47.540
And next is this!

124
00:08:47.540 --> 00:08:49.370
Hup, hup, hup!

125
00:08:50.980 --> 00:08:52.390
But there's more!

126
00:08:54.380 --> 00:08:57.880
Now it's time for the grand finale!

127
00:08:59.660 --> 00:09:01.140
Penjamin!

128
00:09:01.490 --> 00:09:02.550
Are you okay?

129
00:09:02.550 --> 00:09:04.340
Don't push yourself like this!

130
00:09:04.340 --> 00:09:05.450
Shaddup!

131
00:09:05.970 --> 00:09:09.830
You expect me to stop in 
the middle of a show?!

132
00:09:12.280 --> 00:09:15.570
If I die here on stage, then so be it!

133
00:09:15.570 --> 00:09:17.330
Penjamin...

134
00:09:19.070 --> 00:09:20.540
Here I go!

135
00:09:20.540 --> 00:09:22.080
Take a good gander!

136
00:09:23.210 --> 00:09:26.080
Penjamin's going for the hurdle jump!

137
00:09:27.210 --> 00:09:29.460
Hah!

138
00:09:39.060 --> 00:09:40.630
Yeah!

139
00:09:41.210 --> 00:09:42.490
You did it!

140
00:09:42.490 --> 00:09:44.490
That was amazing, Penjamin!

141
00:09:47.130 --> 00:09:48.970
How do you like <i>them</i> apples?!

142
00:09:48.980 --> 00:09:52.820
The Penjamin Show

143
00:09:49.190 --> 00:09:52.820
What'd you think of Penjamin's 
penguin show, Princess?

144
00:09:53.130 --> 00:09:55.530
Not what I expected, really.

145
00:09:56.650 --> 00:10:00.620
But she felt bad

146
00:09:57.900 --> 00:10:00.620
So she confessed
 anyway

147
00:10:03.300 --> 00:10:04.720
Penjamin!

148
00:10:04.720 --> 00:10:06.710
Oh, is that you, Hamungous?

149
00:10:06.710 --> 00:10:08.280
How's it going?

150
00:10:08.280 --> 00:10:10.950
I heard you were here,
so I came to take a look.

151
00:10:10.950 --> 00:10:13.970
I forgot the two of you were pals.

152
00:10:13.970 --> 00:10:14.950
Yeah.

153
00:10:14.950 --> 00:10:19.220
We worked at the same Chinese restaurant 
before we got our big break.

154
00:10:19.490 --> 00:10:21.160
You haven't gotten rusty?

155
00:10:21.160 --> 00:10:22.720
Perish the thought!

156
00:10:22.720 --> 00:10:26.350
Try some of my pepper steak for yourself!

157
00:10:28.950 --> 00:10:30.390
Here you are!

158
00:10:30.390 --> 00:10:31.890
Looks great!

159
00:10:31.890 --> 00:10:33.400
Oh, not too shabby.

160
00:10:33.400 --> 00:10:35.280
Please try some, Penjamin!

161
00:10:35.590 --> 00:10:39.900
You know I can't eat pepper steak, 
on account of being a penguin and all.

162
00:10:39.900 --> 00:10:41.650
Oh, that's right.

163
00:10:41.900 --> 00:10:44.530
You can have both plates then, Krall.

164
00:10:44.530 --> 00:10:45.310
Eh?

165
00:10:46.170 --> 00:10:49.710
<i>It looks good, but two whole plates?!</i>

166
00:10:49.710 --> 00:10:53.150
How about I show off 
some of my skills, too?

167
00:10:53.150 --> 00:10:54.470
Hooray!

168
00:10:56.500 --> 00:11:00.220
You're still the master 
of making fried rice, Penjamin!

169
00:11:00.700 --> 00:11:01.930
There we go!

170
00:11:01.930 --> 00:11:03.720
That looks amazing!

171
00:11:03.720 --> 00:11:05.440
<i>That's all of it!</i>

172
00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:08.270
<i>It was delicious, but I'm stuffed!</i>

173
00:11:08.270 --> 00:11:09.860
But you know...

174
00:11:09.860 --> 00:11:10.910
Oh, right.

175
00:11:10.910 --> 00:11:13.730
You can't eat fried rice, 
being a hamster and all.

176
00:11:18.210 --> 00:11:21.070
T-Time to chow down...

177
00:11:24.910 --> 00:11:26.950
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

178
00:11:27.530 --> 00:11:30.580
Man, I'm bored.

179
00:11:30.580 --> 00:11:33.060
Why don't you work out, then?

180
00:11:33.060 --> 00:11:35.120
Ugh, what a pain.

181
00:11:35.480 --> 00:11:37.400
You say that now...

182
00:11:37.400 --> 00:11:41.210
Don't come crying when you get a flabby 
belly after all that eating and sleeping.

183
00:11:45.600 --> 00:11:48.090
Little Princess.

184
00:11:48.370 --> 00:11:50.080
Master Mama!

185
00:11:51.870 --> 00:11:54.510
Huh? Are you feeling down?

186
00:11:54.510 --> 00:11:57.650
You're walking with 
a heavier gait than usual.

187
00:11:57.650 --> 00:12:00.390
Impressive, Little Princess.

188
00:12:00.390 --> 00:12:02.030
You noticed that?

189
00:12:03.160 --> 00:12:06.480
I am Commander of the 
Imperial Third Legion.

190
00:12:06.480 --> 00:12:10.700
I can easily glean information 
from the sound of someone's footsteps.

191
00:12:11.410 --> 00:12:13.970
Oh, that's amazing.

192
00:12:13.970 --> 00:12:16.660
I wish she could've seen 
Her Highness just moments ago.

193
00:12:16.660 --> 00:12:18.300
Truth be told...

194
00:12:18.660 --> 00:12:23.370
This morning, I broke my favorite mug,

195
00:12:23.370 --> 00:12:26.630
and it's been one small mistake 
after another at work.

196
00:12:27.050 --> 00:12:29.550
Today's just not my day.

197
00:12:29.550 --> 00:12:32.570
Oh, I've had days like those.

198
00:12:32.570 --> 00:12:35.310
So I'm taking off work early today...

199
00:12:35.960 --> 00:12:38.510
and going on an adventure!

200
00:12:38.510 --> 00:12:40.020
An adventure?

201
00:12:40.020 --> 00:12:45.540
An adventure where I go down the streets
I always pass by but have never taken

202
00:12:45.540 --> 00:12:47.130
to see where all of those turns lead me.

203
00:12:47.130 --> 00:12:49.030
Wow, sounds like fun!

204
00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:50.990
Care to join me?

205
00:12:50.990 --> 00:12:52.500
Yeah, I'll go!

206
00:12:52.500 --> 00:12:54.430
It's lit a fire in her heart?!

207
00:13:15.980 --> 00:13:17.980
The water's so clear.

208
00:13:18.250 --> 00:13:19.930
It sure is.

209
00:13:19.930 --> 00:13:23.810
There's a paddy field nearby. 
Is that what this irrigation canal's for?

210
00:13:19.930 --> 00:13:21.650
Ah! I see it!

211
00:13:21.650 --> 00:13:22.830
Oh, it went your way!

212
00:13:22.830 --> 00:13:24.340
Huh? Wait, where?

213
00:13:26.680 --> 00:13:27.960
Right next to you!

214
00:13:27.960 --> 00:13:29.320
I don't see it at all!

215
00:13:29.320 --> 00:13:33.330
It's a little warm today, 
so I bet that feels great.

216
00:13:33.330 --> 00:13:34.000
Yeah.

217
00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:34.990
Oh, right there!

218
00:13:34.990 --> 00:13:36.740
Okay, it's ours!

219
00:13:36.740 --> 00:13:39.290
Awesome, we got it!

220
00:13:39.290 --> 00:13:40.940
Did you catch something?

221
00:13:42.740 --> 00:13:43.830
A crab!

222
00:13:44.120 --> 00:13:46.120
Oh, very nice.

223
00:13:46.120 --> 00:13:47.880
You can find crabs here?

224
00:13:47.880 --> 00:13:48.590
Yeah.

225
00:13:48.850 --> 00:13:50.550
Ricefish as well.

226
00:13:50.550 --> 00:13:52.600
Wow!

227
00:13:52.600 --> 00:13:54.400
Catch you later!

228
00:13:54.400 --> 00:13:56.120
Bye-bye!

229
00:14:12.660 --> 00:14:14.680
What a pretty bird.

230
00:14:15.030 --> 00:14:16.900
So cute!

231
00:14:17.540 --> 00:14:19.960
Little Princess, do you like birds?

232
00:14:19.960 --> 00:14:21.000
Yeah.

233
00:14:21.260 --> 00:14:24.540
But it's not like 
I know what they're called.

234
00:14:24.540 --> 00:14:27.020
So I usually try not to mention it.

235
00:14:28.700 --> 00:14:33.880
You don't have to be an expert 
to say you like something.

236
00:14:34.390 --> 00:14:37.350
Liking things isn't a competition.

237
00:14:40.300 --> 00:14:42.620
Yeah, you're right.

238
00:14:43.740 --> 00:14:46.340
I like birds!

239
00:14:56.970 --> 00:14:59.210
What a funny-looking staircase.

240
00:14:59.210 --> 00:15:00.830
You said it!

241
00:15:00.830 --> 00:15:02.030
Let's climb to the top!

242
00:15:02.030 --> 00:15:04.340
Climb, climb!

243
00:15:19.630 --> 00:15:21.700
We sure have walked a lot.

244
00:15:21.700 --> 00:15:23.550
This has been fun.

245
00:15:23.550 --> 00:15:24.520
Yeah.

246
00:15:26.310 --> 00:15:30.620
<i>That reminds me 
that I was feeling down today.</i>

247
00:15:30.990 --> 00:15:34.280
<i>All this fun on my adventure 
with Little Princess made me forget.</i>

248
00:15:39.580 --> 00:15:41.210
Master Mama!

249
00:15:42.070 --> 00:15:44.080
I haven't been tortured yet today,

250
00:15:44.080 --> 00:15:48.450
and I forgot to get permission to go out, 
so I let Torture know where I was.

251
00:15:48.450 --> 00:15:51.600
Right, since you're a prisoner.

252
00:15:51.600 --> 00:15:56.220
And Torture just told me about a place 
with great tea around here!

253
00:15:56.740 --> 00:15:58.390
She said I can go visit it!

254
00:15:58.390 --> 00:15:59.970
Oh?

255
00:15:59.970 --> 00:16:02.550
That's awesome.

256
00:16:09.840 --> 00:16:10.810
Oh, my.

257
00:16:10.820 --> 00:16:13.820
Gonna check it out now!

258
00:16:11.250 --> 00:16:12.660
What an adorable bird.

259
00:16:13.820 --> 00:16:16.320
The Next Day

260
00:16:19.480 --> 00:16:23.040
<i>An experimental spell went haywire...</i>

261
00:16:23.580 --> 00:16:26.100
<i>turning the princess into a bird!</i>

262
00:16:26.100 --> 00:16:27.490
Surrend!

263
00:16:27.490 --> 00:16:30.070
You fiend! What's the meaning of this?!

264
00:16:30.070 --> 00:16:32.010
Return Her Highness 
to her old self at once!

265
00:16:32.010 --> 00:16:33.720
I'm terribly sorry.

266
00:16:33.720 --> 00:16:38.660
We're looking into it now 
but have yet to determine the cause.

267
00:16:38.660 --> 00:16:39.900
Say it ain't so...

268
00:16:39.900 --> 00:16:42.200
It breaks my heart 
to see Her Highness like this.

269
00:16:42.040 --> 00:16:44.020
Surrend! Surrend!

270
00:16:42.200 --> 00:16:44.730
It must be a terrible 
inconvenience being stuck like that.

271
00:16:44.900 --> 00:16:47.520
Unable to even talk properly...

272
00:16:47.950 --> 00:16:49.740
She can't reveal any secrets like this,

273
00:16:49.740 --> 00:16:52.570
<i>so maybe this is better for the empire.</i>

274
00:16:52.940 --> 00:16:55.050
No, don't think like that, Ex!

275
00:16:55.050 --> 00:16:57.330
There's no way that Her Highness 
is better off this way!

276
00:16:57.600 --> 00:16:59.710
Why is she a bird, anyway?!

277
00:16:59.710 --> 00:17:02.330
I really don't have an answer for that.

278
00:17:02.650 --> 00:17:06.040
Perhaps because she's fond of birds?

279
00:17:06.040 --> 00:17:07.140
I see...

280
00:17:07.140 --> 00:17:07.920
Surrend.

281
00:17:07.920 --> 00:17:09.300
No, that can't be it!

282
00:17:09.300 --> 00:17:11.340
And wait, Her Highness likes birds?

283
00:17:11.340 --> 00:17:13.130
That's news to me!

284
00:17:13.430 --> 00:17:17.410
It seems she mentioned it during 
her adventure with Giant yesterday.

285
00:17:17.410 --> 00:17:21.510
She even sent me a photo of a cute bird.

286
00:17:22.140 --> 00:17:22.980
What?

287
00:17:22.980 --> 00:17:24.570
Was I the only one who wasn't told?

288
00:17:25.100 --> 00:17:28.030
<i>Maybe Her Highness really 
</i>is<i> better off this way...</i>

289
00:17:28.030 --> 00:17:30.280
Surrend! Surrend!

290
00:17:30.960 --> 00:17:33.800
Here's some food 
for the time being, Princess.

291
00:17:33.800 --> 00:17:38.920
I'm not sure what you can eat, 
so here are some nuts I've ground up.

292
00:17:38.920 --> 00:17:40.040
Surrend.

293
00:17:40.040 --> 00:17:41.520
Surrend, surrend.

294
00:17:40.140 --> 00:17:41.210
She's eating it!

295
00:17:41.520 --> 00:17:44.350
What a relief. Do you like it?

296
00:17:44.350 --> 00:17:45.730
Surrend! Surrend!

297
00:17:45.730 --> 00:17:47.270
She's practically a pet now.

298
00:17:48.400 --> 00:17:51.030
The vast majority of polar 
bears are left-handed.

299
00:17:51.030 --> 00:17:53.620
No way! She's folding even in this state?

300
00:17:53.940 --> 00:17:56.020
Why is she giving in as a bird?

301
00:17:56.020 --> 00:17:58.540
Did Her Highness retain full sentience?

302
00:17:58.540 --> 00:18:03.500
No, she can hardly be considered aware
and is acting mostly by instinct.

303
00:18:03.500 --> 00:18:05.320
She's surrendering by instinct?!

304
00:18:05.320 --> 00:18:06.790
This is bad!

305
00:18:06.790 --> 00:18:11.350
She could turn into an endless 
surrender machine at this rate!

306
00:18:11.350 --> 00:18:13.310
Fear not, Ex.

307
00:18:14.120 --> 00:18:17.680
I won't report any information 
gained outside of a torture session.

308
00:18:17.680 --> 00:18:19.070
Going by the book!

309
00:18:19.630 --> 00:18:22.660
Our top priority right 
now should be the princess.

310
00:18:22.660 --> 00:18:25.280
Thank goodness Torture is our inquisitor!

311
00:18:25.670 --> 00:18:27.830
I wanna eat something sweet.

312
00:18:27.830 --> 00:18:29.820
You could learn a thing 
from her, Your Highness!

313
00:18:30.360 --> 00:18:32.380
Something sweet?

314
00:18:32.380 --> 00:18:36.040
What kind of sweet food can a bird eat?

315
00:18:36.040 --> 00:18:37.730
Gâteau au chocolat.

316
00:18:37.730 --> 00:18:39.930
She's got a big attitude for a bird 
with no sentience.

317
00:18:40.210 --> 00:18:42.430
I'm sorry, Princess.

318
00:18:42.430 --> 00:18:46.720
A bird's digestive system cannot 
process gâteau au chocolat.

319
00:18:46.720 --> 00:18:47.810
Surrend?!

320
00:18:47.810 --> 00:18:52.810
Surrend! Surrend! Surrend!

321
00:18:49.560 --> 00:18:52.810
I can prepare it for you 
when you've returned to your old body.

322
00:18:52.810 --> 00:18:54.840
Surrend!

323
00:18:55.370 --> 00:18:57.490
What's going on? Could it be?

324
00:18:57.870 --> 00:19:00.370
Her craving for gâteau au chocolat...

325
00:19:00.370 --> 00:19:04.170
has broken the spell and 
is returning her to her original self?!

326
00:19:04.170 --> 00:19:05.780
Her gluttony knows no bounds!

327
00:19:08.560 --> 00:19:09.620
Not quite!

328
00:19:09.620 --> 00:19:11.040
Surrend!

329
00:19:11.040 --> 00:19:12.560
Biblical levels of gluttony!

330
00:19:15.090 --> 00:19:16.680
Surrend!

331
00:19:18.620 --> 00:19:20.760
Surrend!

332
00:19:21.030 --> 00:19:22.200
I see...

333
00:19:22.200 --> 00:19:25.390
Since it was her desire to eat 
that broke the spell...

334
00:19:25.390 --> 00:19:28.200
Only her body returned to normal.

335
00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:31.320
So she could have a digestive system 
that can process gâteau au chocolat.

336
00:19:32.470 --> 00:19:36.490
Which means that if I offer her food 
that a bird's head cannot eat...

337
00:19:36.490 --> 00:19:38.230
That's it, Torture!

338
00:19:38.230 --> 00:19:39.070
Your Highness!

339
00:19:39.070 --> 00:19:40.180
Surrend?

340
00:19:40.180 --> 00:19:42.350
Here's a tasty rice cracker.

341
00:19:42.350 --> 00:19:45.020
You won't be able to eat this 
with a bird's mouth.

342
00:19:45.020 --> 00:19:45.950
Surrend?!

343
00:19:45.950 --> 00:19:48.610
Surrend!

344
00:19:48.840 --> 00:19:49.830
You did it!

345
00:19:50.110 --> 00:19:51.540
It worked!

346
00:19:53.880 --> 00:19:55.790
A smartphone emoji!

347
00:19:59.030 --> 00:20:01.900
Let's just wait for
 the Hellhorde to figure it out.

348
00:20:01.900 --> 00:20:03.130
I suppose.

349
00:20:03.130 --> 00:20:04.940
Surrend!

