Here! The hilt of the sword is longer!

385
00:22:54.230 --> 00:22:55.630
You're right!

386
00:22:55.630 --> 00:22:58.140
It's so conspicuous, 
yet I didn't notice it at all!

387
00:23:00.220 --> 00:23:03.920
The last one! I can't find 
the last one for the life of me!

388
00:23:03.920 --> 00:23:05.790
Let's look it up online.

389
00:23:05.790 --> 00:23:07.140
Hold it, Sakura-chan!

390
00:23:07.450 --> 00:23:09.620
Let me look a little longer.

391
00:23:11.360 --> 00:23:12.570
<i>That's right.</i>

392
00:23:12.570 --> 00:23:15.510
<i>Senpai always gives her full effort.</i>

393
00:23:15.510 --> 00:23:20.370
<i>That attitude is what's 
behind those flawless tortures of hers.</i>

394
00:23:20.900 --> 00:23:24.470
<i>Despite her experience, 
she never phones it in for a torture.</i>

395
00:23:24.470 --> 00:23:26.880
<i>She always tackles it 
with the utmost sincerity.</i>

396
00:23:27.160 --> 00:23:29.360
<i>That's the Senpai I admire!</i>

397
00:23:30.030 --> 00:23:32.330
I'll see it through to the end with you!

398
